noise_settings.noise.density_offset.help: Affects the average terrain height. A value of 0 produces terrain land height at half the height. Positive values raise the height.

noise_settings.noise.top_slide.size.help: Defines a range of 'Size * Size Vertical * 4' blocks where the existing density and target are interpolated.
noise_settings.noise.top_slide.target.he: The target density. Positive values add terrain and negative values remove terrain.
